  "remarks": "JSC UMZ is a Russian military-industrial state enterprise that develops missile systems, including the Buk-M2 missile system, deployed by the Russian Armed Forces. Moreover, JSC UMZ is part of the Almaz-Antey concern, a Russian state-owned arms manufacturer that develops anti-aircraft defence and cruise missile systems for the Russian military.",
